    <h3>Innovative Technology</h3>
    <p>Sequencing-by-building is an innovative technology allowing the instrument to construct fragments of DNA based on the original sequence without needing to circularise the DNA. Key innovations in optics, computing power, lasers, coatings and microfluidics have opened up endless possibilities for the future of Genomics.</p>        
